text: Stäketskogen Nature Reserve () is a nature reserve in Upplands-Bro Municipality, Stockholm County in Sweden. The nature reserve has been created to protect an area of old-growth mixed coniferous forest. The area is hilly, with glacial till, and has been subjected to a very low degree of forestry. It is a known habitat for several species of endangered insects and bracket fungi. ==References== ==External links== * Category:Nature reserves in Sweden Category:Geography of Stockholm County Category:Tourist attractions in Stockholm County Category:Protected areas established in 1989 Category:1989 establishments in Sweden
